::DarkMouse::

She whispers to Quickstrike,"How are you feeling? I can't see anyone 
down there on the bridge, but that doesn't mean that they aren't 
there. I'll climb down and you cover me. OK?"

The vent was just right for her mouse size.  But since Quickstrike 
was a bit bigge than her, he may have found the vent a bit tight for 
him.  But it was big enought that both bots could get around.

"Has that stuff kicked in yet? You feeling like a million energon 
cubes yet?"
